    "Together, these improvments aim to advance the development of reliable, context-aware, and adaptive defenses against evolving phishing and spam threats.",
    "In this study, we introduced a new, richly annotated dataset of phishing, spam, and legitimate emails, including emotional and motivational labels, rephrased variants, and model-generated samples.",
    "We benchmarked multiple LLMs for emotional and motivational analysis, selected the best-performing model, and conducted a largescale classification experiment across original and rephrased emails.",
    "Below, we summarize the answers to our research questions.",
    "• RQ1: How effectively can LLMs identify emotional strategies and patterns used within email content?"
